---
title: Salsa-Topped Chicken with Sweet Pepper and Roasted Potato Jumble
description: Cheesy, salsa-topped chicken and spiced potatoes bring the feisty fiesta to this Mexican-inspired dinner! This one is sure to please even picky eaters: add more or less salsa, sour cream and green onions depending on everyone's tastes.
